4:
Wonder when Rain will show up? It's
not like him to be late...
6:
Oh well. We're just going to walk
around at the festival, so I guess
there's no rush—
9:
Like I said! A friend's waiting for me,
so I have to go!
12:
I can't go out with you! I already
have plans!
15:
I can't just let my precious angel
leave me so soon!
17:
I'm not asking you to go out with
me! I just wanna... hang out for a
while, okay?
24:
N-never mind! Someone's waiting
for me, so get out of my—
32:
There you are, Alk! Sorry to keep you
waiting, but could you come help
me—
40: Sorry, I don't believe we've met.
46:
You know me! Sublieutenant Rain of
the Gaean Navy! Please, help me!
52:
So your fan club chose that outfit for
you, huh?
56:
I refused so many times, but they
kept insisting this outfit was "the
cutest!"
58:
I know it's Halloween, but I'm a
sublieutenant in the Gaean Navy
now! I should be wearing something
more distinguished!
61:
Even still, the fact that you're
wearing it anyway says something
good about your character.
65:
It wouldn't be right to turn down a
gift like that! What choice did I
have?!
69:
Well... I guess the people got what
they wanted. You seemed pretty
popular out there.
73:
Yeah, and I'm not happy about it!
Besides, I don't think there's really
much demand for these kinds of
get-ups—
82:
Rain! What do you say to taking part
in this?
91:
The event will be on FIRE if you're
part of it, Rain! So please, I'm
begging you!
95:
I appreciate the offer... I think?
But I already have plans with Alk
today.
99: Oh, I see... That's too bad...
104:
Well... If Rain's not into it anyway, I
guess we'll just continue on with our
day as planned—
108:
It's a real shame. The top prize is a
recipe book and Halloween sweets
from a famous patissier in Palpebra.
112:
Sublieutenant Rain. Duty calls. Don't
worry about the plans I had for
today.
122:
This year's Halloween Cosplay
Summit's shaping up to be a great
one!
124:
Next is contestant number two!
You're up, Rain!
128: D-do I really have to do this?
133: Of course! Take it away, Rain!
146: Give me your treats, or you'll regret it!
155: So CUTE! I'm... I'm gonna cry!
165:
Thanks a million, Rain! I would've
never got my hands on this recipe
book without your help!
168:
Why? How did I win? Where is this
demand coming from?!
172:
See, Rain? It's almost annoying how
cute you are! Have some
confidence!
178:
Well... I guess everyone had a good
time, and I also helped you get that
book...
180:
In the end, I made people happy. I
wasn't into this outfit at first, but I'll
have to thank my friend for picking it
out...
183:
You really go with the flow, huh? For
better or worse.
188:
Where'd that come from? Weren't
you praising me a second ago?!
191:
Rainy-Raaain! Congrats on your big
win! Did you see me in the crowd?!
192:
You're the most adorable angel I've
ever seen, Rain!
